{"tid":992550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★突發！$4000申請表格不足　最快下周才有新表格！","createTime":"2019-01-23T09:06:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-23T11:30:44.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a02ad60c21f636649b9278530b233cf28e99790b","tid":992550,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T09:06:37.000Z","msg":"政府派錢4000元的「關愛共享計劃」於周一（21日）開始派發申請表格，惟多區派發點一早出現派罊的情況，亦有人批評所需的證明文件繁複。<br />\n<br />\n深水埗區議員楊彧今日（23日）接受商台節目《在晴朗的一天出發》訪問時稱，早前向局方預留約1,000份表格，加上自行影印約2,000份表格，合共3000份表格派給市民，現時已所餘無幾，惟當局稱需要至本月尾或二月初才可補給。<br />\n<br />\n他認為當局低估需求，又建議局方應簡化住址證明的要求。<br />\n<br />\n補給表格最快需於本月尾至2月頭<br />\n<br />\n深水埗區議員楊彧接受商台節目訪問時稱，兩日以來協助約逾1,000人填寫申請表格，未計及僅前往取表格的市民。他稱早前向當局預留約1,000份表格，而自己額外影印約2,000份，首兩日共約提供3,000份表格供市民取用。惟現僅餘下約300至400份的表格，預料將於今日派罊。他稱曾向當局索取更多表格供市民取用，不過獲回覆稱最快需至本月尾至2月頭才可提供。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/286335/%E6%B4%BE%E9%8C%A24000%E8%9A%8A-%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E8%A1%A8%E6%A0%BC%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%B3-%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E5%BC%95%E8%BF%B0%E7%95%B6%E5%B1%80%E6%9C%80%E5%BF%AB%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E6%89%8D%E6%9C%89%E6%96%B0%E8%A1%A8%E6%A0%BC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F286335%2F%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E9%258C%25A24000%25E8%259A%258A-%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25B6%25B3-%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25BC%2595%25E8%25BF%25B0%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%25B1%2580%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%2589%258D%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%25A0%25BC&d=B443tWVhrLE9WEntoKY0GW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=cdf48de2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/286335/%E6%B4%BE%E9%8C%A24000%E8%9A%8A-%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E8%A1%A8%E6%A0%BC%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%B3-%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E5%BC%95%E8%BF%B0%E7%95%B6%E5%B1%80%E6%9C%80%E5%BF%AB%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E6%89%8D%E6%9C%89%E6%96%B0%E8%A1%A8%E6%A0%BC</a>"},{"pid":"70d68d932da3d1d6758b75af6970da5ae84b407c","tid":992550,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T09:07:51.000Z","msg":"仲炒劉華門票已經out<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現在炒$4000 表格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d1b46a2fc47303cab05f463faf9d18894858d2f","tid":992550,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T09:10:08.000Z","msg":"淘寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8024b98d37b44fb2f59a43311561e9176d31eec","tid":992550,"uid":2590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T09:42:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f56ac2c614091aa5a31e54dabcaa0395d16bcae2","tid":992550,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T11:30:44.000Z","msg":"瘋搶"}]}